tRank provides a score for each line, TopSum provides a distance between the topic distributions of an incremental summary and the original text, and f it provides the fitness of each line. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.00018906593322753906}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.0682811737060547e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 4.172325134277344e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9770230054855347}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9885209798812866}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "(Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004)", "normalizedForm": "Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004", "refKey": 0}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "TextRank", "normalizedForm": "TextRank", "offsetStart": 10, "offsetEnd": 18}, "context": "While for TextRank we rely on the off-the-shelf implementation of (Barrios et al., 2016), in the following we describe the other two methods.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.004931747913360596}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.34893089532852173}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.980232238769531e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9770230054855347}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9885209798812866}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "(Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004)", "normalizedForm": "Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004", "refKey": 0}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "TextRank", "normalizedForm": "TextRank", "offsetStart": 11, "offsetEnd": 19}, "context": "We use the TextRank implementation5 of (Barrios et al., 2016) without removing stop words (lyrics lines in input can be quite short, therefore we avoid losing all content of the line if removing stop words). ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9770230054855347}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.2934207916259766e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9770230054855347}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9885209798812866}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "(Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004)", "normalizedForm": "Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004", "refKey": 0}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "Thumbnail", "normalizedForm": "Thumbnail", "offsetStart": 11, "offsetEnd": 20}, "context": "The Lyrics Thumbnail is computed using String-based distance between text segments to facilitate clustering.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9986052513122559}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 4.708766937255859e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.7881393432617188e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9994286298751831}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9998712539672852}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "Thumbnail", "normalizedForm": "Thumbnail", "offsetStart": 16, "offsetEnd": 25}, "context": "A Lyrics Double Thumbnail consists of two segments: one from the fittest segment cluster (usually the chorus), and one from the second fittest segment cluster (usually the bridge).1", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0008115172386169434}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.00013780593872070312}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.980232238769531e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9994286298751831}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9998712539672852}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "Thumbnail", "normalizedForm": "Thumbnail", "offsetStart": 17, "offsetEnd": 26}, "context": "While the Lyrics Thumbnail is generated from the full segment structure of the lyrics including its duplicate lines, all other models are fed with unique text lines as input (i.e.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.77593594789505}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.104043960571289e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 4.172325134277344e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9994286298751831}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9998712539672852}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "TopSum", "normalizedForm": "TopSum", "offsetStart": 41, "offsetEnd": 47}, "context": "TextRank provides a score for each line, TopSum provides a distance between the topic distributions of an incremental summary and the original text, and f it provides the fitness of each line. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.00018906593322753906}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.0682811737060547e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 4.172325134277344e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9975926876068115}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9885209798812866}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 4.172325134277344e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "TopSum", "normalizedForm": "TopSum", "offsetStart": 41, "offsetEnd": 47}, "context": "Here x \u2208 (S \\ sum(S)) and A \u2208 {TextRank, TopSum, fit}.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9975926876068115}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 4.655122756958008e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.980232238769531e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9975926876068115}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9885209798812866}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 4.172325134277344e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "TextRank", "normalizedForm": "TextRank", "offsetStart": 43, "offsetEnd": 51}, "context": "We also produce two summaries by combining TextRank + TopSum and TextRank + TopSum + Lyrics Thumbnail, to test if summaries can benefit from the complementary perspectives the three different summarization methods take.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.002502918243408203}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.3732495903968811}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.980232238769531e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9770230054855347}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9885209798812866}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "(Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004)", "normalizedForm": "Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004", "refKey": 0}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "TextRank", "normalizedForm": "TextRank", "offsetStart": 49, "offsetEnd": 57}, "context": "Model Nomenclature For abbreviation, we call the TextRank model henceforth M r , the Top-Sum model M s , the fitness-based summarizer M f , model combinations M rs and M rsf , respectively.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.004470169544219971}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.713369369506836e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.980232238769531e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9770230054855347}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9885209798812866}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "(Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004)", "normalizedForm": "Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004", "refKey": 0}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "Thumbnail", "normalizedForm": "Thumbnail", "offsetStart": 49, "offsetEnd": 58}, "context": "Analog to an audio thumbnail, we define a Lyrics Thumbnail as the most representative and repetitive part of the song text.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.006868183612823486}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.000263214111328125}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9994286298751831}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9998712539672852}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "TextRank", "normalizedForm": "TextRank", "offsetStart": 53, "offsetEnd": 61}, "context": "Three of the most popular graphbased summarizers are TextRank (Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004), LexRank (Erkan and Radev, 2004), and (Parveen et al., 2015).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.000209808349609375}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.6656856536865234e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.980232238769531e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9770230054855347}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9885209798812866}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "(Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004)", "normalizedForm": "Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004", "refKey": 0, "offsetStart": 6214, "offsetEnd": 6240}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "TopSum", "normalizedForm": "TopSum", "offsetStart": 56, "offsetEnd": 62}, "context": "8 We also produce two summaries by combining TextRank + TopSum and TextRank + TopSum + Lyrics Thumbnail, to test if summaries can benefit from the complementary perspectives the three different summarization methods take.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.004457831382751465}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.017709970474243164}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.980232238769531e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9975926876068115}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9885209798812866}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 4.172325134277344e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "TextRank + TopSum", "normalizedForm": "TextRank + TopSum", "offsetStart": 65, "offsetEnd": 82}, "context": "We also produce two summaries by combining TextRank + TopSum and TextRank + TopSum + Lyrics Thumbnail, to test if summaries can benefit from the complementary perspectives the three different summarization methods take.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.002502918243408203}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.3732495903968811}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.980232238769531e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.002502918243408203}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.3732495903968811}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.980232238769531e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "TextRank", "normalizedForm": "TextRank", "offsetStart": 70, "offsetEnd": 78}, "context": "We have applied both generic unsupervised text summarization methods (TextRank and a topic-based method we called TopSum), and a method inspired by audio thumbnailing on 50k lyrics from the WASABI corpus.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9393032789230347}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9885209798812866}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.980232238769531e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9770230054855347}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9885209798812866}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "(Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004)", "normalizedForm": "Mihalcea and Tarau, 2004", "refKey": 0}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "Tex-tRank", "normalizedForm": "Tex-tRank", "offsetStart": 75, "offsetEnd": 84}, "context": "This is done to produce less redundant summaries, given that for instance, Tex-tRank scores each duplicate line the same, hence it may create summaries with all identical lines. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0009992718696594238}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.820657730102539e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.980232238769531e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0009992718696594238}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.820657730102539e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.980232238769531e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "Thumbnail", "normalizedForm": "Thumbnail", "offsetStart": 78, "offsetEnd": 87}, "context": "If the second fittest cluster has a fitness of 0, we generate a Lyrics Single Thumbnail solely from the fittest cluster (usually the chorus).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.8297603726387024}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.516674041748047e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.7881393432617188e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9994286298751831}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9998712539672852}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 5.364418029785156e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "Thumbnail", "normalizedForm": "Thumbnail", "offsetStart": 84, "offsetEnd": 93}, "context": "Moreover, we introduce a method inspired by audio thumbnailing (which we dub Lyrics Thumbnail) which aims at creating a summary from the most representative parts of the original song text.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 8.064508438110352e-05}, "created": {"value": 